title: Women Holding Hands Medium Dark Skin Tone
description: Represents two women holding hands, with medium-dark skin tones. It signifies romantic relationships, friendship, solidarity, or companionship between two women.
apple_vendor_description: On Apple devices, this emoji beautifully depicts two women with medium-dark skin tones holding hands, rendered with Apple’s signature glossy 3D shading and smooth gradients. Their hands are shown with soft, rounded edges, conveying a sense of unity and connection through subtle realistic lighting. This emoji is a powerful symbol of love, friendship, and solidarity, often used on Apple devices to celebrate diverse relationships and shared moments.
